      <title>乌克兰陆军司令称俄罗斯在多个领域占据前线主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/ukrainian-army-head-says-russia-dominates-front-in-several-areas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰高级士兵表示，乌克兰东部前线的战斗变得更加激烈，俄罗斯在多条轴线上利用了相对于基辅军队的优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/ukrainian-army-head-says-russia-dominates-front-in-several-areas</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 15:11:14 GMT</pubDate>
