    <item>
      <title>马克龙通过建议核武器来提高国防投入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/macron-raises-europe-defense-stakes-by-suggesting-nuclear-arms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙(Emmanuel Macron)在讨论中加入了核武器，提高了他呼吁建立可靠的欧洲防御的赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/macron-raises-europe-defense-stakes-by-suggesting-nuclear-arms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 14:02:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着伊朗制裁压力加大，拜登抑制天然气价格的策略面临危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/where-are-gas-prices-heading-as-biden-faces-iran-pressure-before-the-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年加油站的天然气成本已经上涨了 18%，但国会正在敦促加强制裁执行力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/where-are-gas-prices-heading-as-biden-faces-iran-pressure-before-the-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 14:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
