    <item>
      <title>小罗伯特·肯尼迪正在吓唬拜登的盟友。他也应该吓唬特朗普。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/rfk-jr-is-scaring-biden-s-allies-he-should-scare-trump-s-too</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登的盟友正在竞相削弱小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪的总统竞选活动，将他的第三方努力视为旨在增加唐纳德·特朗普竞选机会的假马——尽管他广泛的政策立场使他对两国都构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/rfk-jr-is-scaring-biden-s-allies-he-should-scare-trump-s-too</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯访问美国推动加沙停火的“最后机会”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/us-pushes-for-last-chance-of-gaza-ceasefire-as-blinken-visits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周一抵达中东时将加大努力确保加沙停火，这可能是说服以色列取消对南部城市拉法的袭击的最后机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/us-pushes-for-last-chance-of-gaza-ceasefire-as-blinken-visits</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 11:34:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰计划从七月起将公用事业电费削减五分之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/poland-aims-to-cut-utilities-power-tariffs-by-a-fifth-from-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰计划将公用事业公司征收的最高电价削减19%，以降低国家补贴成本，帮助家庭免受电价上涨的全面影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/poland-aims-to-cut-utilities-power-tariffs-by-a-fifth-from-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 10:34:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙准备开启欧洲核防御辩论：孚日晨报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/macron-ready-to-open-europe-nuclear-defense-debate-vosges-matin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统马克龙表示，他愿意讨论核武器，作为建立可靠的欧洲防御的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/macron-ready-to-open-europe-nuclear-defense-debate-vosges-matin</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 09:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>校园反战抗议者从纽约到加利福尼亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-28/campus-anti-war-protesters-dig-in-from-new-york-to-california-as-universities-and-police-take-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日早上，抗议以色列-哈马斯战争的学生们在全国大学校园的帐篷里醒来，计划举行更多抗议活动，要求学校切断与以色列的经济联系，并从被指控煽动冲突的公司撤资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-28/campus-anti-war-protesters-dig-in-from-new-york-to-california-as-universities-and-police-take-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国任命资本市场资深人士担任财务主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thailand-picks-capital-markets-veteran-pichai-as-finance-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理斯雷塔·塔维辛 (Srettha Thavisin) 任命资本市场资深人士皮查伊·春哈瓦吉拉 (Pichai Chunhavajira) 为泰国新任财政部长，这一任命可能会缓解总理与央行之间在货币政策方面的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thailand-picks-capital-markets-veteran-pichai-as-finance-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 04:43:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
